      "comment": "HARA'S MILENA (2) recorded her Best Time this course and distance last time when a 30.37 winner of a Grade 5 in the quickest time on the card. In form and looks the one to beat again. GARRISON (1) is better than last start when fourth (30.77) from Box 2 at Q Parklands over 520m. Has a strong record out of this box with five wins and three minor placings from 11 starts. Bold showing expected. DAINTREE CHIEF (4) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by 4.5 lengths at Q Parklands in a handy 30.06 beating Big Zeal. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Can go close again if runs up to latest figure. MILCHICK (8) placed last start and is in the mix again.",
